============== Passives ===========
Rampage: When the gnoll reduces a creature to 0 hit points with a melee attack on its turn, the gnoll can take a bonus action to move up to half its speed and make a bite attack
Incite Ramage (recharge 5-6): As part of its multiattack, one creature the gnoll can see within 30 ft of it can use its reaction to make a melee attack if it can hear the gnoll and has the Rampage trait
